  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>We have compiled an enticing range of excursions in each destination. Some excursions can be booked in advance when you confirm your holiday and others can be purchased in resort from your resort representative. Details and prices of all our excursions are shown on the resort pages.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>If you haven't taken advantage already, you can arrange your excursions prior to your arrival in resort. Many people prefer to pre-book prior to departure from the UK, enabling them to arrive in resort with minimal organisation required. In addition, if you pre-book more than 4 weeks prior to departure, adding excursions to your booking is free (or £15 if within 4 weeks prior to departure).</p>
<div class="hr hr-spaced"></div>
<h2>Inghams Plus – Sightseeing Savings</h2>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Free Excursions</strong></p>
<p>Take advantage of our special offers in Switzerland and Canada where we include a <strong>Free excursion or activity for Inghams guests</strong>. Look out for trips such as cable cars, sightseeing tours and boat trips on resort pages. </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Half-Price Swiss Travel</strong></p>
<p>The fantastic and scenic Swiss transport network makes exploring independently by bus, rail, boat, cable car or mountain railway a pleasure. We include a <strong>half-price card</strong> entitling you to 50% discounts on a range of day trips from many of our Swiss resorts.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Save up to 10% in Austria</strong></p>
<p>The more you see, the more value you get in Austria! With such a selection of excursion options in Austria, you can take advantage of this extra value.</p>
<ul>
<li>Pre-book 3 excursions and save 10%  </li>
<li>Pre-book 2 excursions and save 5%</li>
</ul>]]></bodyText>
