  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>There is a life-time’s worth of places to explore in every one of our chosen countries. From the major must-do sights to smaller hidden gems, by joining one of our coach excursions you get a feel for the country you are visiting and make the most of your time away. We will show you festivals, natural wonders, history and culture, and your Inghams Rep will be on hand to share their knowledge and make every day out run smoothly.</p>]]></shortDescription>
